data.description: Stunning real log mountain home only minutes from the heart of Edgewood!  Light the wood stove and curl up on the couch as you enjoy being nestled in this serene mountain setting.  Gorgeous open floorpan with amazing loft.  Oversized front deck and an upper back deck have boundless views.  Rustic charm with all the modern amenities including community water.   All this sits on an acre that is fully fenced!   All appliances stay!  Detached 2 car garage in addition to a work-shed with  power.  Desirable Rancho Sandia Subdivision is tucked away but oh so close! This is a turn key opportunity for an amazing property! Would make a fantastic place to call home or could be a perfect vacation home or vacation rental!  Please see supplemental for a list of recent upgrades!
